### Table

##### Default Table

Adding .center class to your table element will center the text inside the table. 
You can also use .text-center on any table element to center the text inside that element.

##### html
----------

```
<table class="center">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>...</th>
      <th>...</th>
      <th>...</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>...</td>
      <td>...</td>
      <td>...</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
```

